### 2. Create `public/robots.txt`

1. Click **"Add file"** again
2. Select **"Create new file"**
3. Type filename: `public/robots.txt`
   - Since `public` folder now exists, it will just add the file there
4. Paste this content:
```
User-agent: *
Allow: /

Sitemap: https://howmuchprotein.in/sitemap.xml
```

5. Click **"Commit changes"**
6. Click **"Commit changes"** again

